{"tid":45073,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]同女女去東京","createTime":"2016-12-18T17:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T16:55:48.000Z","uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6edbd6b7e230393f7811e4402e03d8bf4fb69eb","tid":45073,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"見最近yen跌左<br />\n諗住遲下同女女去東京玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能1 2月去 可能5 6月去<br />\n睇邊個時候得閒d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東京一定會去 可能去5/6日 如果時間多嘅可能會去10日去埋九州名古屋嗰d<br />\n但你地覺得8000銀搞唔搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e26c6d9e9ce68d5073f19ad32534bb3ed854cf6","tid":45073,"uid":5378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"8000我諗你要推條女落火坑先夠錢埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d672c39b82c94b54a82d6c7d4b9f0043844a8bb","tid":45073,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"八千就留喺旺角銀座食放題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa51926fddd170f022446f4b149276de8bb84ba4","tid":45073,"uid":12219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8000我諗你要推條女落火坑先夠錢埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5-6日 一個人$8000洗費 機票酒店另外計都夠既<br />\n2個人就唔洗諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我宜家買左機票2月尾去8日<br />\n$4000 2個人 早去晏就返<br />\n酒店你預$900一晚<br />\n另外我地會去埋箱根玩一泊二食溫泉旅館都要預$1500一個人<br />\n你自己計下呢d基本野夠唔夠錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當地餐餐食拉麵就好平既 但唔知你女女o唔ok同會唔會再shopping 個d la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f474f8abc12c88e025f4e5f5b68134ee04a10d8","tid":45073,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"6c942b6eb07cdedd39e1bd94cdc1ade8552698a2","tid":45073,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"美金呀？"},{"pid":"89eef5b9dd9d9afd8a90f6d72ea1f0a974946dd5","tid":45073,"uid":65615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:34:18.000Z","msg":"8000點夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要買車飛，買野食，買手信，比入場費"},{"pid":"a30b1af75d295125a94356752053a0a6fb81db90","tid":45073,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我對上幾個月先去完東京6日<br />\n都係同女女去<br />\n2個人都洗左40000啦<br />\n仲要唔係餐餐都食好，又唔係買左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db0e7352ad9a02556703346e86572359858d98f","tid":45073,"uid":27908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我對上幾個月先去完東京6日<br />\n都係同女女去<br />\n2個人都洗左40000啦<br />\n仲要唔係餐餐都食好，又唔係買左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係有錢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e1d92881244e03baefb4a80a8e30e5f4707123","tid":45073,"uid":48306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我對上幾個月先去完東京6日<br />\n都係同女女去<br />\n2個人都洗左40000啦<br />\n仲要唔係餐餐都食好，又唔係買左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係有錢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"