016-12-19T01:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>8000係一個人定兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早排0.72果期單拖去咗東京 6日5夜<br />\n唔計機票酒店 都使左HKD$17000<br />\n<br />\n(利申 唔是餐餐豪食 買左唔算太多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好奇想知 點用左 $17000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔是餐餐豪食 但十餐有六餐都有是食靚和牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後女人買下藥妝 買下化妝品咩果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落埋個原宿 <br />\n萬七蚊你估好多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日洗二千幾蚊港紙點會唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本物價都唔係貴香港好多"},{"pid":"13ab4a857c800c58cce6a91c073c3b3e20e55432","tid":45073,"uid":7905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"8000兩個人洗費東京淨食嘢唔買嘢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你去東京近郊 交通費都貴死你啦 <br />\n<br />\n8000去台灣同泰國吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1843e916ce63f6705f2797b451637951b6596b2","tid":45073,"uid":45454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"樓主真係太年輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca43c677b6c8af0af62a64470a40af38fb2fcbd","tid":45073,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"一個人去東京6日5夜$8000一定無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機票來回$1500<br />\n住hostel $250唔洗有一晚, 夾埋5晚我又預多你當你$1500<br />\n淨返一日有成$800, 唔係入去遊樂場的話乜柒都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔出東京的話, 交通費俾撚到盡一日最多咪$200<br />\n仲有$600, 你拎$300去玩, $100食午餐, $200食晚餐, 大丈夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbde07822195f16cce73da4f64b4cb169ee0f23","tid":45073,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人去東京6日5夜$8000一定無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機票來回$1500<br />\n住hostel $250唔洗有一晚, 夾埋5晚我又預多你當你$1500<br />\n淨返一日有成$800, 唔係入去遊樂場的話乜柒都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔出東京的話, 交通費俾撚到盡一日最多咪$200<br />\n仲有$600, 你拎$300去玩, $100食午餐, $200食晚餐, 大丈夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去到咁不如唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48190694f4213ceab8454d343c30b1f72f55515","tid":45073,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個人去東京6日5夜$8000一定無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機票來回$1500<br />\n住hostel $250唔洗有一晚, 夾埋5晚我又預多你當你$1500<br />\n淨返一日有成$800, 唔係入去遊樂場的話乜柒都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔出東京的話, 交通費俾撚到盡一日最多咪$200<br />\n仲有$600, 你拎$300去玩, $100食午餐, $200食晚餐, 大丈夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去到咁不如唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去到點呀, 講丫? 未撚試過咁去唔好出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你住撚過hostel未呀? 有無enjoy過成晚同日本妹吹水呀?<br />\n3000yen晚餐食多幾多好野你又知唔知呀? 又唔撚係叫你食500yen松屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f9e2fbfdc03b1fe1ca2c0a1a6861477de3fcd2","tid":45073,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我對上幾個月先去完東京6日<br />\n都係同女女去<br />\n2個人都洗